author: GameSpot
description:
The legendary fighting series makes its Steam debut with Virtua Fighter 5 R.E.V.O.
Launching on Steam this winter!

Step into the ring with Virtua Fighter 5 R.E.V.O. Based on Virtua Fighter 5 Ultimate Showdown, Virtua Fighter 5 R.E.V.O. gives players an optimized gaming experience in their quest to become the world’s greatest fighter. 

Features:
• Rollback Netcode
• Up to 60fps/4K support
• Gameplay balance adjustments and more
title: VIRTUA FIGHTER 5 R.E.V.O. - Official Opening Cinematic Reveal Trailer

author: GameSpot
description:
Welcome to this episode of Jolly Jenny's weekly news!
Bad news, a warehouse in Blazewood was attacked last night. Good news, by the time the locals found out, the bandits were all knocked out cold!

"Wait, the goods in the warehouse are ours, aren't they?! Lighter!"
"Huh? Where's Lighter?"
"...He's sleeping."
title: Zenless Zone Zero - Lighter Cinematic Character Demo | "TKO"
